{"tid":991834,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"秋冬天出汗/食熱野/去人多既地方會痕","createTime":"2019-01-22T16:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T16:33:40.000Z","uid":22975,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4687830c5773817a8f5c63fc1b3b6ea0488ad2c1","tid":991834,"uid":22975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"我就係患者，當以上情境出現就會出現巨痕由頭到背好似比針吉既痕 <br />\n其實係<span style=\"color: red;\">膽鹼能性蕁麻疹</span><br />\n<br />\n當受熱、精神緊張、攝入熱的食物或飲料，或在運動後，體溫略增，增熱的血流刺激大腦體溫調節中樞，興奮膽鹼能性神經並釋放乙醯膽鹼，如果對這種化學物質過敏，可以出現過敏反應。<br />\n<br />\n詳細內容<br />\n<a href=\"http://cht.a-hospital.com/w/胆碱能性荨麻疹\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcht.a-hospital.com%2Fw%2F%E8%83%86%E7%A2%B1%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7%E8%8D%A8%E9%BA%BB%E7%96%B9&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=53c5d1d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://cht.a-hospital.com/w/胆碱能性荨麻疹</a>"},{"pid":"a39aaa415aa88b2b68727084d598cc3229162520","tid":991834,"uid":22975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"有冇香港既皮膚科/內分泌科既巴打發表下意見"}]}